<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink328">
<l>nuṇmaḻai taḷitteṉa naṟumalar tāayt</l>
<l>taṇṇiya vāyiṉum veyya maṉṟa</l>
<l>maṭavara liṉṟuṇai yoḻiyak</l>
<l>kaṭamutir cōlaiya kāṭiṟan tēṟkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though they are cool, when fragrant flowers scatter </l>
<l>as if rain is drizzling with tiny drops, they still burn for me —</l>
<l>who left behind my sweet innocent girl </l>
<l>and crossed the wilderness </l>
<l>of harsh paths and leave-shedding groves. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
